<li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider clearfix" style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px #e6e6e6; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 13px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px #e6e6e6; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; display: block;">Radcliffe Exploratory Seminar Award, Radcliffe Institute, Harvard University (2016).</span></li>
